figgy.title: There is no way to clear a field value in a numismatic dropdown field

comments.body: This is likely blocked until https://github.com/pulibrary/figgy/issues/3656 is resolved.
I think most of these fields should have a selectable value, whether it is commonly used or not. It will help to reduce noise in the data. My vote is to leave Color as it is.

comments.body: Attributes names and descriptions can't be easily done as these are multi-valued nested forms. It's possible we can add them later, but I would suggest splitting them off into a separate issue of lower priority.
Description previews are not good because of latency involved with the select widget searching thousands of values. I'm going to split these off into a separate ticket with low priority.
